1604
01:55:37,363 --> 01:55:41,766
but I guess I could've been more helpful
with your job and everything, you know.

1605
01:55:43,002 --> 01:55:44,867
Well, why are you...

1606
01:55:44,938 --> 01:55:47,907
puttin' up this wall
where you just tore one down?

1607
01:55:47,974 --> 01:55:51,102
Well...
I changed my mind.

1608
01:55:51,177 --> 01:55:53,941
I don't mean to seem
dense or anything,

1609
01:55:54,013 --> 01:55:58,245
but what's changed?
The air and the light.

1610
01:56:00,620 --> 01:56:03,214
Ed...
Hmm?

1611
01:56:03,289 --> 01:56:05,757
You remember how
you used to tell me...

1612
01:56:05,825 --> 01:56:08,555
you always wanted
two women in your house?

1613
