[Laughing]
Oh, God.

1614
01:56:10,997 --> 01:56:12,658
Yeah.

1615
01:56:12,732 --> 01:56:14,757
Well...

1616
01:56:14,834 --> 01:56:17,769
what if I was
the younger of the two?

